Package KI305.Panasiuk.Lab7

Class Paper

java.lang.Object
KI305.Panasiuk.Lab7.Paper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Item>, Item
public class Paper extends Object implements Item
A class representing a piece of paper that implements the Item interface. It provides methods to get the content of the paper and to print its details. This class also implements the Comparable interface for comparison with other items.

1.0
